Don your Heroic Persona, which includes a set of armor and a shield, and gain {{level:monk}} temporary hit points; it lasts for 1 hr. or until you end it with a bonus action. While active:
You can use a bonus action and 1 ki point to gain {{wisdom:modifier}} temporary hit points;
You can spend 1 ki point after hitting with an unarmed strike to deal 1d10 additional damage;
you can use Charisma for AC calculation even in light or medium armor (difference of {{dex cha diff}});
ability checks and divination spells to determine your true identiy will fail.
You can expend 3 ki points to reuse this feature before a rest.

