Enter an Elemental Form for 1 minute or until you are incapacitated or use a bonus action to end it. While in this form:
You gain flying speed equal to your walking speed;
You resist bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage;
Critical hits against you become normal hits;
You gain {{wisdom:modifier}} temporary hit points at the start of each of your turns.
You can expend 6 ki points to regain this form before a long rest.
